div.p: This is my open-source home play ground. I am very passionate about open-source. Open-source allows me to take and give back to the tech community.
The open-source technologies I use are:

Syncthing - Data replication software
Wireguard - A modern VPN protocol
Keepass v2.x - Password manager
Pfsense - Software firewall
Duplicati - Backup soltuion
Jellyfin - Media server
Calibre - E-Book server
Draw.io - Diagraming tool (this is why you see this diagram)
Rocky Linux - The Linux distribution I use in my labs.
T-Pot - An open source honeypot
